data.description: Discover the epitome of an entertainer's paradise seamlessly blended with the tranquility of a private oasis in this remarkable 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom oversized brick RANCH. Nestled on a sprawling corner lot, this residence spans over 6000 sqft of pure creativity, redefining what most assume a Ranch-style home is. As you step inside, be captivated by the three-season room embraced by mature trees, overlooking the expansive in-ground heated pool, outdoor seating, and a private firepit area. Indulge in luxury as the master bedroom provides direct access to a Jacuzzi, creating a seamless connection to your very own backyard oasis. The interior boasts an inviting eat-in kitchen with Brazilian cherry wood floors, complemented by plush NEW carpeting throughout. A fully finished basement awaits, featuring a commercial sized bar, gym or bedroom, professionally installed Karaoke stage, another bedroom, and a colossal home theater, perfect for hosting unforgettable gatherings. Immerse yourself in the opulence of high-end light fixtures, accent walls, and a master bath adorned with a soaker tub and his-and-her sinks. The gym offers a commercial gas sauna with a steam function, reaching a blissful 180 degrees effortlessly. This home comes complete with a pool table, piano, and a sauna that seamlessly become part of the package. Updates abound, from fresh paint throughout to a new Samsung double-load washer/dryer and a barely used double oven. The 3.5-car garage is equipped with an EV charger, a modern convenience that stays with the home. In the winter months, enjoy stunning subdivision lake views from the living room, transforming this residence into your personal oasis on one floor and an impeccable entertainer's haven on the lower level. Don't miss the chance to make this extraordinary property your own, where luxury, entertainment, and tranquility converge in perfect harmony.
